    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014it\u2019s in pristine, showroom condition and has been babied since day one. Not a single scratch or dent to be found, just pure perfection inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and looks basically brand new, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for you to come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
