    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with its high-revving 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example boasts a factory-correct Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a structurally sound subframe, recently reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates for long-term chassis rigidity. The VANOS system has been meticulously overhauled with Beisan",
